headers.subject: [tosdr:3149] Evernote not blacklisted

subject: Evernote not blacklisted
text:
I use Evernote and am quite satisfied with their view on integrity. So I was surprised to see the warning on TosDR, saying account cannot be deleted - according to the accountkillerblacklist. Well, I checked. Evernote is not blacklisted there (anymore?) And it is possible to kill your Evernote account (yes I did read the terms before signing up, and was already sure). If TosDR rely on other sources, it's necessary to check these out now and then.
Yours, LenaO
